parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering rack and pinion can cause the steering wheel to lock up or become difficult to turn, leading to loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Whining or grinding noises when turning
fluid leaks from the power steering pump or rack
stiff or labored steering
and sudden loss of power assist.

stiff or labored steering
and sudden loss of power assist.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden lock-up of the steering wheel can cause loss of control and increase the risk of accidents.

sudden loss of power assist.
